room_title: Escape room "Zombie Apocalypse" by Escape Rehoboth in Rehoboth Beach
room_address: 20245 Bay Vista Rd. Rehoboth Beach, DE 19971
room_description: The Zombie Apocalypse has finally happened! You’ve been able to survive on your own, but it sure would be nice to be part of a community again. During your travels, you met up with a small group of survivors and you’ve arrived at this abandoned military complex in the hopes of finding temporary shelter and supplies instead of becoming the zombies next meal!!
